chart.description: Time spent writing/reading data file blocks by backends in this database, in milliseconds
chart.name: Block Time
chart.programText:
A = data('pg_stat_database_blk_write_time', filter=filter('metric_source', 'gitlab-postgres'), rollup='latest').publish(label='A')
B = data('pg_stat_database_blk_read_time', filter=filter('metric_source', 'gitlab-postgres'), rollup='latest').publish(label='B')

chart.description: Number of project repositories

chart.programText:

B = data('pg_stat_table_n_tup_del', filter=filter('table_name', 'project_repositories'), rollup='latest').publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A-B).publish(label='C')

B = data('pg_stat_database_tup_inserted', filter=filter('metric_source', 'gitlab-postgres'), rollup='latest').publish(label='B')

chart.description: Number of Git HTTP request-response cycles currently being handled by gitlab-workhorse.
chart.name: GitLab Workhorse Active Sessions
Database Size
chart.programText:
A = data('pg_total_relation_size_bytes', rollup='latest').sum().publish(label='A')
B = (A).timeshift('1h').publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A).timeshift('1d').publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = ((A-B)/B*100).publish(label='D')
E = ((A-C)/C*100).publish(label='E')

chart.description: The total number of catched errors.
chart.name: GitLab Runner Errors

chart.description: Day-over-Day Change in Requests
chart.name: Requests/sec 24h Change %
chart.programText:
A = data('nginx_vts_server_requests_total', filter=filter('code', 'total'), rollup='average').rateofchange().publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).timeshift('1d').publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A/B-1).scale(100).publish(label='C')

chart.description: Number of connections in reading headers, waiting to send response, and writing response states
chart.name: Active Connection States
chart.programText:
A = data('nginx_vts_main_connections', filter=filter('status', 'reading'), rollup='latest').publish(label='A')
B = data('nginx_vts_main_connections', filter=filter('status', 'writing'), rollup='latest').publish(label='B')
C = data('nginx_vts_main_connections', filter=filter('status', 'waiting'), rollup='latest').publish(label='C')

chart.description: Number of builds in pipeline processing queues
chart.name: Build Pipeline Processing Queues
chart.programText:
A = data('sidekiq_queue_size', filter=filter('name', 'pipeline_processing:build_queue'), rollup='latest').publish(label='A')
B = data('sidekiq_queue_size', filter=filter('name', 'pipeline_processing:build_finished'), rollup='latest').publish(label='B')
C = data('sidekiq_queue_size', filter=filter('name', 'pipeline_processing:build_success'), rollup='latest').publish(label='C')
D = data('sidekiq_queue_size', filter=filter('name', 'pipeline_processing:ci_build_schedule'), rollup='latest').publish(label='D')

chart.description: Number of committed/rolled back transactions in this database
chart.name: Transactions
chart.programText:
A = data('pg_stat_database_xact_commit', filter=filter('metric_source', 'gitlab-postgres'), rollup='latest').publish(label='A')
B = data('pg_stat_database_xact_rollback', filter=filter('metric_source', 'gitlab-postgres'), rollup='latest').publish(label='B')

chart.name: Requests/Connection
chart.programText:
A = data('nginx_vts_server_requests_total', filter=filter('code', 'total'), rollup='latest').delta().publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('nginx_vts_main_connections', filter=filter('status', 'active'), rollup='latest').publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A/B).publish(label='C')
